snippet.title: LazerGrrl release trailer
snippet.description:
LazerGrrl is a free broswer game that combines the fury of Bomberman with the strategy of an RTS. Play now!
Free WebGL version: https://sandwich-generation.itch.io/lazergrrl-lite
Full Windows version (in early access):  https://sandwich-generation.itch.io/lazergrrl

Join our Discord where you can, chat to the devs, give feedback, swap tactics with other players, and most Importantly, take place in our monthly tournament. You could be crowned the best player in the world!!
https://discord.gg/CxtnKrG

Landing Page
https://lazergrrl-landingpage.netlify.com/
